//     efficiency. It uses an 8-bit radix, meaning the count arrays (of size 256)
//     are small enough to comfortably fit in L1 cache, minimizing latency.
//     Furthermore, its internal implementation uses block-based techniques to
//     improve data locality during the histogramming phase.
